    "hjy À e iθ ŷji, where y = HðcÞx and ŷ = ĤðcÞx are the true and predicted vectors of measured signals, respectively, upon coherent injection of a pilot signal x 2 C N T × 1 into the system with metasurface configuration c. We use N T pilot signals drawn from a complex-valued random distribution with normally distributed real and imaginary parts, and the pilot signals are the same for all metasurface configurations in the calibration data set.",
